. Serve immediately."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"Chicken and Marinade","content":["1 whole uncooked chicken (40-48 oz, approx. 2 ½-3 pound chicken)","1 organic lemon, halved","1 yellow onion, quartered (approx. 5.5 oz)","3 garlic cloves","¾ in. fresh ginger, peeled (approx. 0.5 oz)","3 green onions, trimmed and quartered (approx. 2 oz)","3 sprigs cilantro, stems and leaves","2 tbsp miso","2 tbsp soy sauce","1 tbsp mirin"]},{"title":"Broth","content":["1 yellow onion (approx. 5.5 oz), halved","1 - 2 fresh chilies (e.g. serrano), deseeded if preferred","3 - 4 shiitake mushroom, dried, sliced","1 tsp sesame oil","1 tbsp chicken stock paste (see Tip)","55 oz water","4 eggs, washed","14 oz udon noodles, fresh (see Tip)","4 oz carrot, halved lengthways and sliced (½ in.) (approx. 1-2 carrots)","3 ½ - 5 ½ oz baby corn, canned, drained and halved","5 ½ - 7 oz broccolini (approx. 1 bunch) trimmed and cut into pieces (1½-2 in.)","1 - 2 tsp salt, to taste","1 - 2 green onions, trimmed and cut into thin slices, to garnish","2 - 3 sprigs cilantro, leaves only, torn, to garnish","1 tbsp ready-made fried onions, to garnish (optional)","1 nori sheet, cut into thin strips, to garnish (optional)"]}],"id":"r106919","imageLink":"https:\/\/4.bp.blogspot.com\/-3BoFf7-j158\/XZMybQxIqzI\/AAAAAAAAakw\/QCFl9q6YQBYFhFIrRrLKMzbud5kg2EmAACLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_CmNyGOhP1yAMYf5_.png","title":"Asian Chicken Noodle Soup","publishedAt":"2017-03-17T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"49 g","fat":"22 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"83 g","calories":"3255 kJ \/ 778 kcal"},"usefulItems":"thermometer","hintsAndTricks":["Please refer to <i>The Basic Cookbook<\/i> for the Chicken Stock Paste recipe.","Remove noodles from packaging, place into Varoma tray and rinse noodles under warm water to separate. Set aside.","Find Asian ingredients at your local Asian specialty store.","To shred chicken in Thermomix: place up to 32 oz chicken meat into mixing bowl and shred <strong>5 sec\/\/speed 3.<\/strong>